---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Terms of Service | Devin Larkin" description="Terms of service for Devin Larkin's freelance copywriting services.">
  <section class="py-16 px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    
    <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Review and customize these terms for your specific needs -->
    
    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-6">
      <p class="text-gray-600 italic">Last updated: [Insert Date]</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Agreement to Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing or using this website, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use this website.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Services</h2>
      <p>This website provides information about freelance copywriting services. Specific project terms, deliverables, and pricing will be agreed upon separately for each engagement.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All content on this website, including text, graphics, and design, is the property of Devin Larkin unless otherwise noted. You may not reproduce or distribute this content without permission.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>This website and its content are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We are not liable for any damages arising from your use of this website.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about these terms, please contact us through the contact form on our website.</p>
    </div>
    
    <p class="mt-12 p-4 bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded text-yellow-800 text-sm">
      <strong>Note:</strong> This is placeholder content. Please review and customize these terms of service to accurately reflect your business practices and comply with applicable laws.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
